<content type="html" xml:base="https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=1209&amp;p=10641#p10641"><![CDATA[
The problem with FCEU is that it only supports <strong>three</strong> "colour emphasis" modes at once on the screen: "no bits", "all bits", and "some bits" (i.e. any other combination, but only the <em>first</em> one it encounters).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Sat Mar 11, 2006 1:28 pm</p><hr />
